snippet.title: Her Majesty's SPIFFING Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Coming December 2016: https://store.steampowered.com/app/488770
Enlist in 'Her Majesty's Special Planetary Investigative Force For Inhabiting New Galaxies' in the graphic adventure game 'Her Majesty's SPIFFING'. 

For PC/ Mac/ SteamOS/ Xbox One and PlayStation 4. 

Presskit: press.billygoat.tv
